                     <interp inst="t17961130-32-person310" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn. - I keep the Equestrain Coffee-house, joining the Royal Circus, opposite the Obelisk; I have known the prisoner two years; I never knew any dishonesty of him; he has three small children; he has worked for me, and I have lent him as much as two guineas at a time.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17961130-32-person311">
                  WILLIAM
                   KETTLIN
               <interp inst="t17961130-32-person311" type="surname" value="KETTLIN"></interp>
