                  </persName>
             sworn. - I live at No. 94, Norton-street, Mary-le-bonne; the prisoner lived next door to me two years; I never heard any other but a good character of him; I have trusted him when he was out of work with coals and wood, he always paid me again.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17961130-32-person312">
